casebody.data:
Friday, November 17, 2000

MOTION DOCKET

00-1457. State ex rel. Commt. for Referendum of Ordinance No. 3543-00 v. White.

In Mandamus. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of mandamus regarding an expedited election matter. Upon consideration of relators’ motion for protective order,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for protective order be, and hereby is, denied, because the motion was filed after the action complained of had occurred.
